additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Before every use, TEST YOUR SKIN REACTION by applying and removing the product to a small part of the area you wish to treat, following the directions for use. If after 24 HOURS there is no adverse reaction, continue to use. If you experience any smarting/tingling during use, remove the product immediately using the back of a used strip, Perfect Finish wipe or baby oil and then rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, seek medical advice. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN - Retain outer pack. Read and follow all precautions and directions before use.
